stock_lot_expiry
================

It is a module for Tryton application platform that allow to define expiry
dates (Life Date, Expiry Date, Removal Date and Alert Date) to Stock Lots.

It also adds an integer field in Product for each date, to define the margin:
when a lot is created the dates are computed using these fields as days from
the current date.

Installing
----------

See INSTALL

